Do me a favor and stay away from that boy.

258
00:14:20.250 --> 00:14:21.416
Sarah. go with him.

259
00:14:23.750 --> 00:14:24.958
Menzi.

260
00:14:25.041 --> 00:14:27.250
is this your way of showing me
you're a man now?

261
00:14:27.750 --> 00:14:30.041
So every time I leave this house.

262
00:14:30.708 --> 00:14:33.958
I need to get a nanny
to look after you guys?

263
00:14:34.750 --> 00:14:36.083
You were supposed to be a man.

264
00:14:36.708 --> 00:14:38.000
Take your sister to her room.

265
00:14:38.833 --> 00:14:40.916
-Mpume. Let's go.
-Hmm?

266
00:14:43.625 --> 00:14:46.375
Mm-mmm. mm-mmm. mm-mmm.
You're not going anywhere.

267
00:14:46.458 --> 00:14:49.208
Stay here and clean up
the mess you guys have made.

268
00:14:51.916 --> 00:14:53.125
Let's go. my love.

269
00:14:53.208 --> 00:14:54.291
Yeah. let's go.

270
00:15:22.833 --> 00:15:25.166
Damn it. man!

271
00:15:25.250 --> 00:15:27.541
Lindani. didn't you see my phone
when you were cleaning?

272
00:15:27.625 --> 00:15:30.666
Mm-mmm. maybe Sis' Ntombi knows.
She was here in the morning.

273
00:15:31.250 --> 00:15:32.250
I've already asked her.

274
00:15:32.333 --> 00:15:33.875
She doesn't know. Lindani.

275
00:15:33.958 --> 00:15:35.916
Goodness. Can't you guys hear
that you're making noise?

276
00:15:36.000 --> 00:15:37.375
I can't find my phone.

277
00:15:38.000 --> 00:15:39.250
Have you tried calling it?

278
00:15:40.250 --> 00:15:42.291
Give me your phone.
I'll check on Find My iPhone.

279
00:15:42.375 --> 00:15:44.375
Ah. geez. What's up with you?

280
00:15:45.208 --> 00:15:48.000
Say please. Why don't you ask me nicely?

281
00:15:48.083 --> 00:15:49.416
Gosh.

282
00:15:50.416 --> 00:15:52.416
-Hi.
-Hi.

283
00:16:06.083 --> 00:16:07.291
Knock. knock.

284
00:16:07.375 --> 00:16:09.375
-How are you. Ma?
-Yes. Mpume.

285
00:16:09.458 --> 00:16:10.833
Cuz. is Freedom around?

286
00:16:10.916 --> 00:16:12.958
-What do you want from my brother?
-My phone is missing.

287
00:16:13.041 --> 00:16:14.333
Find My iPhone says it's in Soweto.

288
00:16:14.416 --> 00:16:18.416
So. if it says it's in Soweto
does it mean Freedom stole it?

289
00:16:18.500 --> 00:16:22.083
No. Ma. I'm here to ask Free and Sarah
if they haven't seen my phone.

290
00:16:22.166 --> 00:16:24.333
You came to ask Sarah and Freedom?

291
00:16:24.416 --> 00:16:25.791
Doesn't Lindani also live in Soweto?

292
00:16:25.875 --> 00:16:27.791
-Why don't you ask your friend?
-Don't you start with me.

293
00:16:27.875 --> 00:16:29.250
Calm down.

294
00:16:29.333 --> 00:16:31.416
Isn't your father rich?

295
00:16:31.500 --> 00:16:33.041
Can't he buy another phone.

296
00:16:33.125 --> 00:16:35.875
-since you lost the one you had?
-What does that have to do with you?

297
00:16:35.958 --> 00:16:38.791
I think I partied too hard last night.

298
00:16:38.875 --> 00:16:42.750
You see. today's hangover…

299
00:16:42.833 --> 00:16:43.833
Eish.

300
00:16:44.541 --> 00:16:46.708
Feels like I was hit by a bus.

301
00:16:47.833 --> 00:16:49.708
Oh. wow.

302
00:16:49.791 --> 00:16:51.666
We've got the entire Destiny's Child
in here.

303
00:16:51.750 --> 00:16:53.708
-What's up?
-Freedom. my phone's missing.

304
00:16:54.375 --> 00:16:56.291
-Okay?
-Oh. come on. I know you took my phone.

305
00:16:56.375 --> 00:16:57.875
Hey. hey!

306
00:16:57.958 --> 00:17:00.291
You came all the way
from the Gomoras' house

307
00:17:00.375 --> 00:17:02.541
-just to tell me this shit?
-Okay. fine.

308
00:17:02.625 --> 00:17:04.708
Let's go to the cops
and ask them to help us find it.

309
00:17:04.791 --> 00:17:07.791
I don't have a problem at all.
Do what you want.

310
00:17:07.875 --> 00:17:11.291
I'll even accompany you
to the police station.

311
00:17:11.958 --> 00:17:13.666
Mpume. get out of here.

312
00:17:13.750 --> 00:17:15.583
-Piss off.
-Don't tell her to piss off. Sarah.

313
00:17:15.666 --> 00:17:17.791
-I said get the hell out of here!
-We're leaving anyway.

314
00:17:17.875 --> 00:17:18.916
-Piss off!
-My goodness.

315
00:17:19.000 --> 00:17:20.375
-What's wrong with this child?
-I said leave!

316
00:17:20.458 --> 00:17:22.083
Ma. let's carry on.
Don't mind this nonsense.

317
00:17:22.166 --> 00:17:24.708
-I said leave! Get out!
-I want my phone.

318
00:17:24.791 --> 00:17:26.166
Ugh. Ugh!

319
00:17:26.250 --> 00:17:28.625
Ma. add more flour.

320
00:17:28.708 --> 00:17:30.958
They're just hungover. these ones.
That's all.

321
00:17:34.000 --> 00:17:35.083
Add more flour. Ma.

322
00:17:38.458 --> 00:17:42.083
That party should never
happened under Menzi's watch.

323
00:17:42.166 --> 00:17:44.500
He should've stopped it.
That's what I'm saying.

324
00:17:44.583 --> 00:17:46.916
Menzi forgets that he's actually a Gomora.

325
00:17:47.000 --> 00:17:48.333
-Okay.
-Who did he take after?

326
00:17:48.416 --> 00:17:50.333
-Definitely not me.
-Come on.

327
00:17:50.416 --> 00:17:52.666
I want Menzi to run J&J one day.

328
00:17:53.166 --> 00:17:55.958
That boy. He's way too soft.

329
00:17:56.041 --> 00:17:58.208
They're good kids. they are.

330
00:17:58.291 --> 00:17:59.375
They need to grow up.

331
00:18:00.750 --> 00:18:02.166
They must do better.

332
00:18:02.750 --> 00:18:06.833
I think that you also need to remember
that these kids.

333
00:18:06.916 --> 00:18:09.875
the year we were apart.
was a really hard year for them.

334
00:18:10.458 --> 00:18:13.541
The kids.
they really went through a lot as well.

335
00:18:15.000 --> 00:18:16.291
Yes. But I'm back now.

336
00:18:18.375 --> 00:18:19.375
Right?

337
00:18:22.333 --> 00:18:23.666
Listen.

338
00:18:24.208 --> 00:18:26.000
I have a request here.

339
00:18:26.083 --> 00:18:29.250
Can we no longer talk about
how you and I were separated?

340
00:18:37.333 --> 00:18:38.791
-Okay.
-There we go.

341
00:18:40.416 --> 00:18:42.208
-Listen.
-Mmm.

342
00:18:42.291 --> 00:18:46.166
Can I ask you to please excuse me.
I need to go to the bathroom.

343
00:18:46.250 --> 00:18:47.333
-Should I accompany you?
-Excuse me.

344
00:18:47.416 --> 00:18:49.166
-Accompany where?
-Mm-hmm.

345
00:18:49.250 --> 00:18:51.875
I don't need you to accompany me.
but I'll be very quick.

346
00:18:51.958 --> 00:18:53.916
-Mmm. Hurry back.
-Okay?

347
00:18:54.416 --> 00:18:57.125
-I'm coming back. Okay.
-Hurry.

348
00:19:21.458 --> 00:19:22.458
Minister.

349
00:19:23.708 --> 00:19:27.458
Ah. Comrade Gomora. How are you. cadre?

350
00:19:27.541 --> 00:19:29.416
-All is well. comrade.
-Good. good. good.

351
00:19:29.500 --> 00:19:30.916
-Great. great.
-Hey.

352
00:19:31.000 --> 00:19:33.166
I see that you also have company.

353
00:19:33.708 --> 00:19:35.958
-Hello.
-Hello to you too.

354
00:19:36.041 --> 00:19:37.333
Mmm.

355
00:19:37.416 --> 00:19:40.583
As the old saying goes.
one man's loss is another man's gain.

356
00:19:40.666 --> 00:19:42.541
-Oh?
-Well. I've taken her in.

357
00:19:42.625 --> 00:19:44.333
And she works in my department now.

358
00:19:44.416 --> 00:19:46.500
-She's doing a stellar job.
-Aw.

359
00:19:46.583 --> 00:19:48.916
She's a dedicated and hard worker.

360
00:19:49.000 --> 00:19:50.833
Mmm. Ah. yes. She really is.

361
00:19:50.916 --> 00:19:53.083
Yes.

362
00:19:54.375 --> 00:19:56.291
Oh. sorry. Number one.

363
00:19:57.333 --> 00:19:59.708
Cadre. yes. yes. Hello.

364
00:20:01.500 --> 00:20:05.541
Well. if you will excuse me.
I need to go powder my nose.

365
00:20:08.458 --> 00:20:10.958
Wait.

366
00:20:11.041 --> 00:20:13.041
-Are you fucking him?
-Ah…

367
00:20:13.125 --> 00:20:15.416
-Are you fucking the minister?
-I don't fucking answer to you anymore.

368
00:20:15.500 --> 00:20:17.250
-Oh?
-In case you've forgotten.

369
00:20:17.833 --> 00:20:19.750
Tell me. Jonasi.

370
00:20:21.250 --> 00:20:24.083
Your wife. won't she be wondering

371
00:20:24.166 --> 00:20:27.166
where you are right now? Hmm?

372
00:20:27.250 --> 00:20:28.541
The father of her children.

373
00:20:29.583 --> 00:20:30.708
Huh?

374
00:20:31.666 --> 00:20:33.000
Don't insult me.

375
00:20:33.083 --> 00:20:34.458
I'm insulting you?

376
00:20:53.208 --> 00:20:55.416
I want you to return Mpume's phone.

377
00:20:55.500 --> 00:20:57.791
But Ma. I don't know
where Mpume's phone is. though.

378
00:20:57.875 --> 00:20:58.875
Sarah.

379
00:21:04.125 --> 00:21:05.125
Look at me.

380
00:21:26.000 --> 00:21:27.583
Listen here. boy.

381
00:21:29.375 --> 00:21:30.791
Why did you…

382
00:21:31.791 --> 00:21:35.916
let Mpume and her friends
turn my house into a madhouse?

383
00:21:36.666 --> 00:21:37.958
Jonasi.

384
00:21:38.041 --> 00:21:40.583
-I thought we already spoke about this?
-No. love.

385
00:21:41.666 --> 00:21:43.333
I want Menzi to answer.

386
00:21:45.458 --> 00:21:49.958
Yes. Dad.
I tried to stop them. You can ask Mpume.

387
00:21:50.041 --> 00:21:52.041
-Mpume!
-I'm asking you.

388
00:21:52.625 --> 00:21:54.375
You're the firstborn son.

389
00:21:54.458 --> 00:21:58.958
So why are you acting weak
when you're my son?

390
00:21:59.041 --> 00:22:01.416
You haven't been the man
of this house for the entire year.

391
00:22:01.500 --> 00:22:02.916
At least Menzi's trying.

392
00:22:05.208 --> 00:22:06.208
Excuse me?

393
00:22:08.791 --> 00:22:10.166
What did you say to me?

394
00:22:11.500 --> 00:22:12.791
My love.

395
00:22:12.875 --> 00:22:15.583
-Who do you think you're talking to?
-Oh. you want to be a father now?

396
00:22:15.666 --> 00:22:16.958
You walked out on us. Dad.

397
00:22:17.041 --> 00:22:18.333
Have you forgotten?

398
00:22:34.875 --> 00:22:36.458
Hmm.

399
00:22:37.666 --> 00:22:39.208
I've seen it all.

400
00:22:42.583 --> 00:22:44.583
How the mighty have fallen.

401
00:22:53.833 --> 00:22:55.541
Jo!

402
00:22:57.250 --> 00:22:59.250
Don't you ever talk to me like that.
Understood?

403
00:22:59.333 --> 00:23:00.333
Jonasi.

404
00:23:00.416 --> 00:23:02.000
I'm not one of your buddies!

405
00:23:02.583 --> 00:23:04.125
Do you hear me. Mpume?

406
00:23:08.541 --> 00:23:11.166
You. stop being a weakling.

407
00:23:12.500 --> 00:23:13.708
Toughen up.

408
00:23:14.583 --> 00:23:15.875
-Stand up when I'm talking to you!
-Stop!

409
00:23:15.958 --> 00:23:18.000
-Stop being weak!
-Leave him alone!

410
00:23:20.541 --> 00:23:21.833
You're hurting him!

411
00:23:21.916 --> 00:23:24.375
Jonasi. stop!

412
00:23:26.166 --> 00:23:28.208
Do you really wanna kill him?

413
00:23:30.916 --> 00:23:32.166
Menzi. are you okay?

414
00:23:33.125 --> 00:23:34.250
Are you okay. bro?

415
00:23:38.083 --> 00:23:39.666
It's going to be okay.

416
00:23:40.916 --> 00:23:41.916
It's okay.

417
00:23:47.875 --> 00:23:49.208
It's okay.

418
00:23:50.458 --> 00:23:53.875
It's okay. my boy.

418
00:23:54.305 --> 00:24:54.298
